{"tid":1516390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"帝吧係FB度打算死灰復燃！","createTime":"2019-08-29T14:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T14:40:19.000Z","uid":291448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"231452307933609067c424749def62dc159b42c5","tid":1516390,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/byst6Zk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbyst6Zk.png&h=6ace7621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前幾日 無意中比我搵到個咁嘅Group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  㩒入去一望發現全部都係藍絲、五毛 有D唔排除係帝吧成員黎添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部圍威喂係咁講我地示威者點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之就係講埋晒啲歪理 <br />\n<br />\n大家係時候要做嘢啦 一人一舉報 收呢個Group皮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7bfc547e94ceae5a28b2789a4b3883756ffb6ee8","tid":1516390,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"b69b74fc9a982352bde4e761212a142c97fd2810","tid":1516390,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>反欺凌<br />\n保護警察兒女 你我有責</strong></span><br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n各位中小學生 為左反欺凌 保護警察兒女<br />\n如果有確鑿證據證明邊位同學老豆老母係警察既話記得要<br />\n1.搵人放佢大頭相上黎<br />\n2.寫埋住邊區<br />\n3.寫埋讀咩學校<br />\n等市民可以隨時留意住佢地有冇比人欺凌 係有需要既時候可以保護佢地<br />\n<br />\n因為欺凌係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔局限係校園</span></span>架<br />\n而家市民咁仇警 有人可能會作出自然反應係街上做小動作搞警察兒女<br />\n例如:<br />\n1.唔小心撞佢出馬路<br />\n2.警察兒衝紅燈個陣唔小心女擋住佢唔比佢上行人路<br />\n3.唔小心踼/撞佢落樓梯<br />\n4.係街拍蚊個陣唔小心打中佢<br />\n5.係巴士唔小心擋住佢唔比佢落車<br />\n6.係巴士/小巴唔小心唔讓開比佢入去靠窗位坐<br />\n7.係巴士/小巴唔小心唔讓開比佢離開個靠窗位<br />\n8.係行人路/過馬路個陣唔小心&quot;KICK&quot;跌佢<br />\n9.唔小心擋住LIP口唔比佢入升降機<br />\n10.警察兒女趕返學搭LIP個陣 唔小心撳哂咁多層<br />\n11.係佢要上車/追車個陣唔小心扮健身撚當街捉住佢扮SALE野唔比佢走 <br />\n12.係街上唔小心撞佢落花槽<br />\n13.唔小心撞佢部手機落地<br />\n14.唔小心撞佢手上拎住既其他野落地<br />\n15.唔小心倒瀉野食/野飲落佢地件校服到<br />\n16.唔小心倒瀉野食/野飲「入」佢地個書包到<br />\n17.係鋪頭入面唔小心放左啲未比錢既野入佢個袋到<br />\n18.係佢行過個陣唔小心屋企倒屎水/污糟水落樓<br />\n19.唔小心打開佢書包拉鍊 等佢啲野跌哂出黎<br />\n20.唔小心放啲蛇蟲鼠蟻入佢書包 <br />\nETC.<br />\n<br />\n大家見到有人咁人既話記得要保護佢地 就算啲警察兒女幾忙幾趕時間都要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉住佢地</span></span>幫佢地報警 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比佢地走</span></span><br />\n你地知香港警察做野幾有效率架啦 一個人日日等幾次39分鐘<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都唔係好嘥時間姐</span></span><br />\n如果佢地自己打電話想搵人幫手 千祈唔好唔小心轟佢部手機落地然後踢到母雷公咁遠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1516112/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1516112/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1516100/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1516100/page/1?post=2</a>"},{"pid":"406d2d61ad63ddb6b451454973b7c6b6e2567681","tid":1516390,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:21:15.000Z","msg":"搵人加佢個group啦"},{"pid":"c3228d8832f6f6a71d3791970c02478db3351029","tid":1516390,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"17f27ffd5403c89f3fc42f2d824f119c6c0f9408","tid":1516390,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:40:19.000Z","msg":"一齊聲討帝吧"}]}